description.en: Prom is a modular ZkEVM Layer 2 that enables interoperability across various chains, including both EVM and non-EVM compatible networks. Prom submits its proof of transaction to the additional chains on top of the chosen Settlement chain, building the bridge between ecosystems.

ico_data.short_desc: Prometeus Network is a secure and decentralized ecosystem designed to solve real-world problems in data brokerage
